{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01EFcVxgCMwfTD53ZxEm32aP","type":"tool_result","content":"100\t  secret: Buffer,\n101\t  entropy: Buffer,\n102\t  matchPdaBytes: Buffer,\n103\t  algoVer: number,\n104\t): Buffer {\n105\t  return createHash(\"sha256\")\n106\t    .update(secret)\n107\t    .update(entropy)\n108\t    .update(matchPdaBytes)\n109\t    .update(Buffer.from([algoVer]))\n110\t    .digest();\n111\t}\n112\t\n113\t// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n114\t// Fee allocation + referral earnings hook\n115\t// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n116\t\n117\t/**\n118\t * After a game settles, write one `fee_allocation_events` row per unique\n119\t * player (referred or not), and an additional `referral_earnings` row for\n120\t * referred players.\n121\t *\n122\t * For each unique player: look up profile + referral link ŌåÆ compute the\n123\t * deterministic fee split via `calculateFeeAllocation` ŌåÆ write the\n124\t * allocation row. If a referrer is present, also write the legacy\n125\t * `referral_earnings` row.\n126\t *\n127\t * Errors are logged but never bubble ŌĆö accounting must not fail settlement.\n128\t * Idempotency: `fee_allocation_events` UNIQUE on (source_type, source_id,\n129\t * wallet) plus `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` in `insertFeeAllocation`;\n130\t * `referral_earnings` UNIQUE on (referee_user_id, round_id).\n131\t */\n132\texport async function recordReferralEarnings(\n133\t  db: Db,\n134\t  params: {\n135\t    roundId: string;\n136\t    gameType: string;\n137\t    feeBps: number;\n138\t    referralDefaultRateBps: number;\n139\t    players: Array<{ wallet: string; wagerLamports: number }>;\n140\t  },\n141\t): Promise<void> {\n142\t  const { roundId, gameType, feeBps, referralDefaultRateBps, players } = params;\n143\t\n144\t  // Deduplicate players (Pot Shot can have multiple entries per player)\n145\t  const playerWagers = new Map<string, number>();\n146\t  for (const p of players) {\n147\t    playerWagers.set(p.wallet, (playerWagers.get(p.wallet) ?? 0) + p.wagerLamports);\n148\t  }\n149\t\n150\t  for (const [wallet, wagerLamports] of playerWagers) {\n151\t    try {\n152\t      const refereeProfile = await db.getProfileByWallet(wallet);\n153\t      const link = refereeProfile\n154\t        ? await db.getReferralLinkByRefereeUserId(refereeProfile.user_id)\n155\t        : undefined;\n156\t\n157\t      const referrerRateBps = link\n158\t        ? await db.getReferrerRate(link.referrer_user_id, referralDefaultRateBps)\n159\t        : 0;\n160\t\n161\t      const feeLamports = Math.floor((wagerLamports * feeBps) / 10_000);\n162\t      const allocation = calculateFeeAllocation(feeLamports, referrerRateBps);\n163\t\n164\t      await db.insertFeeAllocation({\n165\t        sourceType: gameType,\n166\t        sourceId: roundId,\n167\t        gameType,\n168\t        wallet,\n169\t        userId: refereeProfile?.user_id ?? null,\n170\t        wagerLamports,\n171\t        feeLamports,\n172\t        referrerUserId: link?.referrer_user_id ?? null,\n173\t        referralRateBps: referrerRateBps,\n174\t        referralLamports: allocation.referralLamports,\n175\t        promotionsLamports: allocation.promotionsLamports,\n176\t        profitLamports: allocation.profitLamports,\n177\t      });\n178\t\n179\t      if (link && refereeProfile) {\n180\t        await db.insertReferralEarning({\n181\t          referrerUserId: link.referrer_user_id,\n182\t          refereeUserId: refereeProfile.user_id,\n183\t          referrerWallet: link.referrer_wallet,\n184\t          refereeWallet: wallet,\n185\t          roundId,\n186\t          gameType,\n187\t          wagerLamports,\n188\t          feeLamports,\n189\t          referrerEarnedLamports: allocation.referralLamports,\n190\t          referrerRateBps,\n191\t        });\n192\t\n193\t        logger.info(\"referral earning recorded\", {\n194\t          roundId,\n195\t 